data.description: Spectacular single story home in the northwest with PAID OFF SOLAR! Monthly power bills are $15! This darling property boasts  a formal living and dining area upon entry with real hardwood floors, an updated kitchen with stainless farmhouse sink and new quartz countertops, and a three car garage with epoxy floors. The primary retreat is separate from the rest and is enormous with plenty of space for a home gym, home office, or hobby room. Generous walk in closet and updated spa-like shower complete this space. Two secondary bedrooms share a jack-and-jill bath, with the latter of the two having built in desks, double doors and access to the rear yard.  Out back you can entertain in style with a built in bbq island with granite countertops, pergola patio cover, and serene landscaping.  Welcome home!
